{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-95","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">security incident</span> je događaj koji može biti opasan za bezbednost ili zaštitu kompanije ili organizacije. Na primer, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">A security incident like a stolen password needs to be reported immediately</span>.</p>\n<p>Zapamtite o <span class=\"highlighted-text\">harm</span> i <span class=\"highlighted-text\">harmful</span>:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Harm</span> To znači štetu ili povredu osobi ili stvari. Odnosi se na uzrokovanje loših efekata ili izlaganje osobe ili stvari opasnosti. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Touching hot surfaces can cause harm.</span> - To znači da dodirivanje vruće površine može izazvati povredu ili štetu.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Harmful</span> je pridev koji se koristi za opisivanje nečega što može izazvati štetu. To znači opasnost ili rizik na način kojim može uzrokovati štetu ili povredu. Na primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Smoking is harmful to health.</span> - Ovo pokazuje da pušenje može uzrokovati zdravstvene probleme ili štetu.</p>\n<p>Ovi pojmovi se često koriste za diskusiju o bezbednosti i riziku, posebno u kontekstima kao što su zdravlje, bezbednost i životna sredina.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks/task-95"},"questions":[{"text":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">security incident</span> šta je ovo?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Redovni sastanak kompanije.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Security incidents</span> je o sigurnosnim rizicima, a ne o redovnim sastancima.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Proslava u kancelariji.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Security incidents</span> Odnose se na bezbednosne probleme, a ne na proslavu.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Pokretanje novog projekta.</p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Security incidents</span> radi se o riziku, a ne o pokretanju projekta.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Problem ili događaj koji može uticati na bezbednost.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null}],"solution":4}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"interview-room2.png","characters":[{"character":"Linda","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"2.1-4.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":40.84,"finishTimestamp":42.98},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":3.14,"dialogue":{"text":"Do we have to report every security incident?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":3.64,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 95","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/#learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks","dashedName":"task-95","certification":"a2-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a2-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-a-typical-workday-and-tasks","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextCh